        "text": "# The roles\n            \n            1) The Scribe : is the one who's writing the content. He/she is collecting all the information/content about the event and he /she retrancripts by writing.\n            \n            2) The Iconographer : it's the person who's in charge to illustrate the event. His/her task is to find on the Internet or to take picture of the event and to select the more appropriate to illustrate what's the scribe is writing. this role have also the job to put the right references about the picture (author...)\n            \n            3)The empathetic-skeptic : this person is the one who criticize or congratulate some element or content about the event. \n            \n            4) The sourcerer : this role involves someone to double check all the information (Scribe and the empathetic-skeptic). He/she have to find articles, conversations, forum about the topic about and try to find and complete the writing by good sources, and if there is a polemic,  try to find what is about)\n            \n            5) the Pollinator : this role have 2 (or 3)task : \n                -find on Internet communities, forums, chats, associations... where the topic is discuss and interesting people\n                -feed those places with the final commun work\n             (   - observe what's happening once the content is distrubuted)\n             \n             6) Summarian (Animator) \n             \n             7) Audio poet"
