 -follows-up with the posts he made during the week that follows the event, to keep the conversation on and help it grow.\n\n- **The Summarian** (Animator): \n     -integrating all the contents and making them coherent with each others, especially by summarizing them \n(be it through drawings, text or audio format) and proposing a coherent esthetics to put them altogether.\n\n- **The Audio Poet**: \n    -runs 2' interviews with the participants of the event to fuel the Story with different voices and viewpoints\n    -*Sina to invent and propose playful easy to make audio formats*\n\n- **The Newage Mapper**:\n    -proposes insightful visualizations (be them digital datavisualization or handmade drawings) to give the future readers of the Story a sense of the atmosphere, spirit and mood of the event"
